# Post-Fix Build Workflow

After any fix in this project:

- Commit the fix.
- Push the commit to `main`.
- Trigger the Android production EAS build with clear cache.
- Move on immediately after the build is queued. Do not wait for the build to complete.

Use this build command exactly:

```bash
cd "/Users/apple/Desktop/FUTURE APPS/Wscars/artifacts/westcars" && npx eas build --platform android --profile production --clear-cache
```

The developer monitors builds independently at:
https://expo.dev/accounts/davidsarb/projects/westcars/builds
